org.cloudgraph.recognizer

Class GraphRecognizerSupport

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cloudgraph.recognizer.GraphRecognizerSupport

  • public class GraphRecognizerSupport
extends java.lang.Object
    Delegate for graph recognizer expression classes. This class is not thread safe and should not be shared across multiple expression class instances.

    0.5.3
